nodes.text: A human male fighter was a member of the Partisans shortly after the formation of the Galactic Empire. Serving under Saw Gerrera, the fighter was one of many rebels who refused to accept the Empire's rule and went into hiding in Onderon's jungle. He was killed when the Empire sent an Elite Squad to attack a rebel camp in the hopes of killing Gerrera while attempting to start up an LAAT/le patrol gunship.
